# Graphify
# Commit the rendered graph (graph.json, graph.html, GRAPH_REPORT.md,
# manifest.json) so any agent or contributor has the same map without
# re-running extraction. Keep transient work files, the per-developer cache,
# and cost telemetry out.
/.graphify_*
graphify-out/.*
graphify-out/cache/
graphify-out/cost.json
